name: A charm of good luck and positivity
description:
May this Diwali bring a lot of joy, happiness, positivity and prosperity in your life. Wish you good health and fortune. Wish you a very happy Diwali. 
(Diwali also known as the festival of Lights is an auspicious Indian festival that is celebrated across India. On this day everyone spends time with the family, shares happiness, positivity, sweets and lights diyas or lamps.)
